<div class="page-content">
  <div class="section-label">Education</div>
  <h1>Reading Lists</h1>
  
        <p>Curated reading lists for students and researchers at different stages. Each list is organized by topic and difficulty level.</p>
        <hr class="divider"/>
        <h2>Beginner — Foundations</h2>
        <p>Start here if you are new to polymer science or chromatography.</p>
        <div class="cards-grid">
          <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">📖</div><h3>Polymer Chemistry Basics</h3><p>Odian, G. <em>Principles of Polymerization</em>, 4th ed. Wiley, 2004.</p></div>
          <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">📖</div><h3>Introduction to HPLC</h3><p>Snyder, L.R. et al. <em>Practical HPLC Method Development</em>, 2nd ed. Wiley, 1997.</p></div>
          <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">📖</div><h3>Polymer Molecular Weight</h3><p>Mori, S. &amp; Barth, H.G. <em>Size Exclusion Chromatography</em>. Springer, 1999.</p></div>
        </div>
        <hr class="divider"/>
        <h2>Intermediate — Polymer IC</h2>
        <p>For researchers with some background in polymer analysis.</p>
        <div class="cards-grid">
          <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">📖</div><h3>Interaction Chromatography</h3><p>Pasch, H. &amp; Trathnigg, B. <em>Multidimensional HPLC of Polymers</em>. Springer, 2013.</p></div>
          <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">📖</div><h3>Critical Conditions Theory</h3><p>Gorbunov, A.A. &amp; Skvortsov, A.M. <em>Adv. Colloid Interface Sci.</em>, 62, 31–108, 1995.</p></div>
          <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">📖</div><h3>PolyCrit Overview</h3><p>Wang, Y. et al. <em>Analytical Chemistry</em>, 94(18), 2022. (Open access)</p></div>
        </div>
        
